name: Six Shooter
background: A special W-Engine modeled after a revolver. It can apparently load six bullet-shaped condensed Ether batteries, which release a significant amount of power when fired. It is said that as long as you carry this W-Engine, you will be able to spontaneously learn how to whistle and will occasionally reference old movies in a cowboy voice.
skill: The equipper gains a Charge stack every 3s, stacking up to 6 times. When launching an EX Special Attack, consumes all Charge stacks, and each stack increases the Daze inflicted by 4%/4.6%/5.2%/5.8%/6.4%.
